                  </li>
                  <li>Increased mobile builder usage by 30%.</li>
                  <li>Reduced mobile-related support tickets by 80%.</li>
                </ul>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-layout__main-panel-content">
          <div class="content-layout__main-panel-content-left">
            <span style="font-weight: 500;"> Intern UI/UX Designer</span>
            <p>LeadSquared</p>
            <p>Jun 2022 – Jun 2023</p>
          </div>
          <div class="content-layout__main-panel-content-right">
            <ul>
              <li>
                <span style="font-weight: 500;">Design System Migration</span>
                <ul class="sub-list">
                  <li>
                    Spearheaded a 6-month migration from Adobe XD to Figma
