              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="content-layout__main-panel-content-left">
            <span style="font-weight: 500;">User-Centric Design</span>
          </div>
          <div class="content-layout__main-panel-content-right">
            <ul style="margin-bottom: 0;">
              <li>User Research, Usability Testing, User Journey Mapping</li>
