            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="content-layout__main-panel-content-left">
            <span style="font-weight: 500;">Go-to-Market & Enablement</span>
          </div>
          <div class="content-layout__main-panel-content-right">
            <ul>
              <li>
                Customer Onboarding, Sales Enablement, Marketing Campaigns
