              <li>
                Improved delivery predictability and stakeholder transparency.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- ABOUT SECTION -->
      <section class="content-layout__main-panel opacity" id="final">
        <div class="content-layout__main-panel-header">
          <span> About</span>
        </div>
        <div class="content-layout__main-panel-content">
          <div class="content-layout__main-panel-content-left">
            <span style="font-weight: 500;">Background</span>
          </div>
          <div class="content-layout__main-panel-content-right">
            <ul>
              <li>
                APM II with 3+ years in building and scaling B2B SaaS CRM and
                Marketing Website Builder platforms.
              </li>
              <li>
                Former Product Designer with strong UX and systems-thinking
                foundation; drives data-informed product strategy and
                cross-functional execution.
              </li>
              <li>
                B.Tech in Computer Science and Engineering with deep frontend
                expertise, enabling effective collaboration with design and
                engineering teams.
              </li>
